束到 `architecture_constraints`，并把最容易跑偏的替代实现写入 `forbidden_implementations`。\\n\\n## 1. System Shape\\n\\n- 交付形态：`independent_microservice`。\\n- 运行方式：`http_service` + `worker` + `scheduled_job`。\\n- 部署单位：独立服务进程；后续实现必须提供生产启动入口和部署入口。\\n- 生产入口最低要求：HTTP server entry、scheduler worker entry、cleanup job entry、配置加载入口。\\n- 当前状态：仓库保留产品、契约、架构和测试文档；不保留任何已完成的业务实现、测试证据或旧运行 trace。\\n\\n## 2. API Boundary\\n\\n- 外部入口：HTTP，契约来源为 `contracts/openapi.yaml`。\\n- 子系统接入：仅通过 HTTP/Feign 调用统一导出平台，不加载业务 JAR，不直接写平台表。\\n- Public operation 完成条件：每个公开 operation 必须能追踪到 route/handler、service、repository 或外部 adapter、测试和证据路径。\\n- 禁止状态：只有 service class、领域函数或单元测试时，不得声明 API 需求完成。\\n\\n## 3. Data Boundary\\n\\n- 持久化：生产路径使用 MySQL 或等价关系型数据库；任务、注册配置、锁租约、批次检查点、文件元信息、审计日志都必须有 schema/migration。\\n- Repository 策略：生产 repository 必须走真实持久化边界；`InMemory*`、mock repository、fixture repository 只能用于单元测试。\\n- 数据访问：平台只允许访问注册配置声明的只读数据源或数据中台，禁止执行调用方传入的原始 SQL。\\n- 数据一致性：幂等键、配置快照、任务状态机、DB 锁租约和审计写入必须有可验证约束。\\n\\n## 4. Async And Worker Boundary\\n\\n- 调度方式：MySQL 轮询 + DB 抢锁。\\n- 锁模型：`lockOwner + lockExpireAt + leaseRenewedAt`，时间判断以数据库时间为准。\\n- 默认租约：5 分钟，worker 只能在批次边界续租。\\n- 接管规则：租约过期后的实例接管延续当前 `attemptNo`，从最近持久化批次检查点继续。\\n- 重试规则：只有 FAILED 重试递增 `attemptNo`；PENDING/EXECUTING 重试必须拒绝。\\n\\n## 5. Test Double Policy\\n\\n- `InMemory*` 允许范围：unit tests only。\\n- Mock 允许范围：外部依赖不可用时可作为临时单测替身，但不能作为验收证据。\\n- 生产完成证据：必须包含 API/handler 测试、DB repository 或 migration 验证、worker/lease 验证、`git diff --check`。\\n- 若真实 MySQL、对象存储或第三方依赖不可用，任务必须记录 `BLOCKED - 需要人工介入`，不得用内存实现冒充通过。\\n\\n## 6. Forbidden Implementations\\n\\n- 禁止把 `InMemory*`、mock、fixture repository 或领域原型作为生产实现完成。\\n- 禁止只有 `src/*/service.ts` 而没有 HTTP route/handler、server entry 和 API 集成测试。\\n- 禁止只有调度 class 而没有 worker entry、DB 锁 schema、repository 原子抢锁和租约测试。\\n- 禁止只有 OpenAPI 契约或文档而声明 `feature_impl` 完成。\\n- 禁止只运行 `git diff --check` 就声明 `feature_impl` 完成。\\n- 禁止把采购订单样板写成平台特例接口；样板必须复用标准 registry、query、file、audit 链路。\\n\\n## 7. Architecture Fitness Checks\\n\\n后续脚手架任务必须创建 `arch:check` 或等价命令。最低检查项：\\n\\n- 生产 HTTP server entry 存在。\\n- scheduler worker entry 和 cleanup job entry 存在。\\n- `contracts/openapi.yaml` 的公开 operation 有 route/handler 和测试映射。\\n- 生产入口没有引用 `InMemory*`、mock repository 或测试 fixture。\\n- MySQL schema/migration 覆盖 task、registry、lease/checkpoint、file metadata、audit log。\\n- `feature_impl` 任务的 `test_command` 包含架构检查、affected tests 和 `git diff --check`。\\n\\n## 8. Definition Of Done\\n\\n- 当前任务的 `architecture_constraints` 已复制本文件相关条目。\\n- 当前任务的 `forbidden_implementations` 覆盖最容易跑偏的替代实现。\\n- Stage 1 Review 先审查架构形态，再审查业务规格。\\n- 完成声明能说明 production path、test double 和 BLOCKED 依赖边界。\\n\\r\\n\\n succeeded in 730ms:\\n# Requirement Interface Matrix：统一导出平台\\n\\n\\u003e 用于把需求映射到后端 API、调度能力、状态和证据路径。\\n\\n## 1. 需求到能力映射\\n\\n| Requirement ID | 需求摘要 | 对应能力 | 状态 | 验收入口 |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n| FR-001 | 创建导出任务 | `POST /api/export/tasks` | PENDING | AC-001 |\\n| FR-002 | 查询任务详情/进度 | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}` | PENDING / EXECUTING / COMPLETED / FAILED | AC-002 |\\n| FR-003 | 下载导出文件 | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download` | COMPLETED / EXPIRED | AC-003 |\\n| FR-004 | 查询任务历史 | `GET /api/export/tasks` | default / empty / permission_denied | AC-004 |\\n| FR-005 | 调度和并发控制 | Scheduler + DB lock | PENDING / EXECUTING | AC-005 |\\n| FR-006 | 大数据分片导出 | Worker + file service | EXECUTING / COMPLETED | AC-006 |\\n| FR-007 | 注册导出任务 / 启停 / 配置 | `POST /api/export/registries` + registry/config APIs | default / disabled / permission_denied | AC-007 |\\n| FR-008 | 集中查询模板契约 | registry/config + datasource/query template | default / invalid_template / datasource_error / query_error | AC-008 |\\n| FR-009 | 权限、脱敏、签名 | auth + data scope + masking + download guard | permission_denied / masking_error | AC-009 |\\n| FR-010 | 审计与失败追踪 | audit log + task event log | all | AC-010 |\\n| FR-011 | 过期清理 | cleanup job | EXPIRED | AC-011 |\\n| FR-012 | 取消和重试 | cancel/retry API | CANCELED / PENDING / FAILED | AC-012 |\\n| FR-013 | 幂等、执行尝试、锁租约和配置快照 | create API + Scheduler + task snapshot | default / conflict / processing / error | AC-013 / AC-014 / AC-015 / AC-016 |\\n| FR-014 | 采购订单导出样板 | purchase-order query template + platform export flow | default / empty / long_content / error | AC-017 / AC-018 / AC-E022 / AC-E023 |\\n| FR-008/FR-010/FR-013 | 查询执行上下文与追踪 | query executor + task event log | default / error | AC-019 / AC-020 |\\n| FR-003/FR-006/FR-011 | 文件临时对象、发布和校验 | file service / OSS | default / error / expired | AC-021 / AC-E026 |\\n\\n## 2. 反查说明\\n\\n- 平台负责任务、调度、下载、审计、注册启停、配置同步、集中查询、字段映射、脱敏、文件生成和清理。\\n- 子系统只负责调用平台任务接口，传递认证上下文和符合注册参数 schema 的业务查询参数。\\n- 下载能力默认签名 URL，必要场景支持流式下载；两种模式都必须携带文件元信息。\\n- `FR-004` 历史查询的正式筛选维度为 `taskCode`、`status`、`createdBy`、`createdAtRange`、`fileFormat`、`subsystemCode`；测试层如已先出现更细筛选项，应标记为分析阶段假设而不是既定事实。\\n- `FR-008` 查询模板契约由注册配置声明数据源、参数 schema、参数化查询模板、字段映射、脱敏策略、数据范围约束、游标字段、排序规则、批大小、行数阈值、保留期和支持格式。\\n- `FR-012` 取消与重试边界为：PENDING 可取消，FAILED 可重试，EXECUTING 取消按批次边界收口；PENDING/EXECUTING 重试返回非法状态错误且不得重复派发执行。\\n- `FR-013` 要求创建幂等、执行尝试、锁租约和配置快照形成同一条审计链路；配置变化不得改变已创建任务的执行口径。\\n- `FR-014` 是一期样板模块合同，不新增平台特例逻辑；它用于证明标准 registry、集中查询模板、调度、文件、权限、审计和下载链路能被一个业务场景完整验证。\\n\\n## 3. 接口证据字段\\n\\n| 需求 | 最小证据字段 / 行为 | 说明 |\\n| --- | --- | --- |\\n| FR-003 | `downloadUrl`、`expiresAt`、`fileName`、`fileSize` 或等价 stream 元信息 | 用于证明下载保护和文件元信息可追踪 |\\n| FR-004 | `taskCode`、`status`、`createdBy`、`createdAtRange`、`fileFormat`、`subsystemCode` | 正式历史查询筛选维度 |\\n| FR-007 | `taskCode` 唯一、`enabled`、并发上限、保留期、单文件行数阈值、最大导出量、支持格式策略 | 注册配置必须能被查询和同步 |\\n| FR-008 | `datasourceCode`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`parameterSchemaDigest`、`fieldMappingDigest`、`maskingPolicyDigest`、`cursorField` | 用于证明集中查询模板、字段映射和脱敏策略可追溯 |\\n| FR-009 | `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope`、`requestId`、`dataScopeExpression` | 统一认证上下文和数据范围约束最小字段 |\\n| FR-010 | `taskId`、`taskCode`、`subsystemCode`、`operatorId`、`action`、`result`、`errorCode`、`requestId`、发生时间 | 审计日志最小字段 |\\n| FR-012 | `attemptNo` 或等价执行尝试序号、内部取消标记、最终状态 | 用于证明重试不丢审计链路、取消不暴露内部状态 |\\n| FR-013 | `clientRequestId`、`idempotencyScope`、`requestDigest`、`configSnapshotDigest`、`attemptNo`、`lockOwner`、`lockExpireAt`、`leaseRenewedAt` | 用于证明幂等、防重复执行、配置快照和锁租约行为 |\\n| FR-006/FR-013 | `cursorField`、`lastCursor`、`processedCount`、`filePartNo`、`batchSize`、`batchRowCount`、`retryCount`、`backoffMs` | 用于证明游标分页、锁接管、批次执行和查询重试证据 |\\n| FR-014 | `taskCode=purchase-order-export`、`subsystemCode=purchase`、`datasourceCode`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`createdAtRange`、`orderStatus`、`supplierId`、`purchaseOrgId`、`keyword`、字段定义、敏感字段脱敏策略、`cursorField=orderId` | 用于证明采购订单样板集中查询合同可执行 |\\n| FR-008/FR-010/FR-013 | `taskId`、`attemptNo`、`requestId`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`datasourceCode`、`batchCheckpoint` | 用于证明查询执行上下文和审计串联 |\\n| FR-003/FR-011 | `tempStorageKey`、`publishedStorageKey`、`checksum`、`checksumVerifiedAt`、`publishedAt`、`deliveryReadyAt` | 用于证明临时对象、发布对象、校验和下载准备状态可追踪 |\\n\\n## 4. 错误映射\\n\\n| 场景 | 对外状态 | 错误码 | 验收入口 |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n| 查询模板不存在或不合法 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` | AC-E011 |\\n| 数据源不可用或凭证不可用 | `FAILED` | `DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE` | AC-E012 |\\n| 查询执行失败 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E013 |\\n| 查询批次重试耗尽 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E020 |\\n| 查询模板或字段映射与任务快照冲突 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` 或 `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | AC-E024 |\\n| 字段映射不合法 | `FAILED` | `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | AC-E014 |\\n| 批次字段、顺序或脱敏结果不合法 | `FAILED` | `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` 或 `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | AC-E025 |\\n| 脱敏规则配置或执行失败 | `FAILED` | `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | AC-E022 |\\n| 文件渲染失败 | `FAILED` | `EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR` | AC-E027 |\\n| OSS 上传失败 | `FAILED` | `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | AC-E005 |\\n| 文件发布前校验失败 | `FAILED` | `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | AC-E026 |\\n| 采购订单游标缺失、重复或非递增 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E023 |\\n\\n## 5. 缺口\\n\\n| Gap ID | 缺口 | 处理方式 |\\n| --- | --- | --- |\\n| GAP-001 | 样板模块字段与表头 | 采购订单导出样板覆盖订单号、订单状态、供应商、采购组织、采购员、创建时间、总金额、币种和脱敏后的联系人信息 |\\n| GAP-002 | 统一认证上下文字段 | 最小字段锁定为 `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope`、`requestId`；联调只确认字段来源和透传方式 |\\n| GAP-003 | 查询性能基线 | 采购订单样板以 10 万行导出作为基线证据，记录总耗时、批大小、分片数和查询重试情况 |\\n| GAP-004 | OSS bucket/path、签名有效期和文件校验值生成方式 | bucket 由环境配置；path 默认 `exports/{subsystemCode}/{taskCode}/{yyyyMMdd}/{taskId}/{attemptNo}/{fileName}`；签名 URL 默认 10 分钟；校验默认 `SHA-256` |\\n| GAP-005 | 采购订单样板合同是否足够驱动实现和测试 | 已锁定 taskCode、subsystemCode、查询条件、字段顺序、敏感字段、游标字段、边界数据和压测证据 |\\n\\r\\n\\n succeeded in 769ms:\\nopenapi: 3.0.3\\ninfo:\\n  title: Export Platform API Contract\\n  version: 1.0.0\\n  license:\\n    name: Internal\\n    url: https://example.invalid/internal-license\\n  description: |\\n    CONTRACT-001 defines the public API contract for FEAT-EXPORT-PLATFORM-001.\\n    The API consumes authentication context from upstream services and exposes\\n    only official task statuses: PENDING, EXECUTING, COMPLETED, FAILED,\\n    CANCELED, EXPIRED.\\nservers:\\n  - url: /api\\n    description: Relative platform API base path\\ntags:\\n  - name: ExportTasks\\n    description: Task creation, detail, history, download, cancel and retry APIs.\\n  - name: ExportRegistries\\n    description: Export task registry, enable/disable and configuration APIs.\\nsecurity:\\n  - OperatorId: []\\n    TenantId: []\\n    RoleCodes: []\\n    OrgScope: []\\n    RequestId: []\\nx-contract-implementation-trace:\\n  description: |\\n    CONTRACT-REVIEW-001 requires every public operation to stay traceable to\\n    later HTTP handler, persistence, worker, audit, file and test obligations.\\n    Paths below are planned implementation targets, not current implementation evidence.\\n  operations:\\n    createExportTask:\\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks\\n      requirements: [FR-001, FR-009, FR-013]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-001, AE-009, AE-014]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/create-export-task.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_idempotency, export_registries, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: [scheduler must consume committed PENDING task]\\n      audit: [CREATE]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.create.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.create.api.test.ts\\n        - tests/db/export-task-idempotency.repository.test.ts\\n    listExportTasks:\\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks\\n      requirements: [FR-004, FR-009, FR-010]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-004, AE-009, AE-010]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/list-export-tasks.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_files, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: []\\n      audit: [QUERY_HISTORY]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.list.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.visibility.api.test.ts\\n    getExportTask:\\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}\\n      requirements: [FR-002, FR-010, FR-013]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-002, AE-010, AE-013]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/get-export-task.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_events, export_task_attempts, export_task_files]\\n      worker: [batch checkpoint and lease fields are worker-produced evidence]\\n      audit: [DETAIL_VIEW]\\n      file: [file metadata must exclude unpublished objects]\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.detail.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.detail.api.test.ts\\n    downloadExportTask:\\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download\\n      requirements: [FR-003, FR-009, FR-010]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-003, AE-009, AE-021]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/download-export-task.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_files, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: []\\n      audit: [DOWNLOAD]\\n      file: [file service must validate published object, checksum, expiry and delivery mode]\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.download.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/file/export-file-download.guard.test.ts\\n    cancelExportTask:\\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel\\n      requirements: [FR-012, FR-010]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-012]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/cancel-export-task.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_events, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: [EXECUTING cancel closes at a persisted batch boundary]\\n      audit: [CANCEL_REQUEST, CANCEL_DONE]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.cancel.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/worker/export-task-cancel-boundary.test.ts\\n    retryExportTask:\\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry\\n      requirements: [FR-012, FR-013, FR-010]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-012, AE-013]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/retry-export-task.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_attempts, export_task_events, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: [retry enqueues a new attempt only for FAILED tasks]\\n      audit: [RETRY_REQUEST]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.retry.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/db/export-task-attempt.repository.test.ts\\n    createExportRegistry:\\n      http: POST /api/export/registries\\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-009]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/create-export-registry.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: []\\n      audit: [REGISTRY_CREATE]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.create.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/api/export-registries.create.api.test.ts\\n    listExportRegistries:\\n      http: GET /api/export/registries\\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-009]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/list-export-registries.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions]\\n      worker: []\\n      audit: [REGISTRY_QUERY]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.list.contract.test.ts\\n    getExportRegistry:\\n      http: GET /api/export/registries/{taskCode}\\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-013]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/get-export-registry.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions]\\n      worker: []\\n      audit: [REGISTRY_DETAIL]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.detail.contract.test.ts\\n    updateExportRegistry:\\n      http: PUT /api/export/registries/{taskCode}\\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-013]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/update-export-registry.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: [updated config applies only to newly created tasks]\\n      audit: [REGISTRY_UPDATE]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.update.contract.test.ts\\n        - tests/db/export-registry-snapshot.repository.test.ts\\n    enableExportRegistry:\\n      http: POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/enable\\n      requirements: [FR-007]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/enable-export-registry.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_registries, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: []\\n      audit: [REGISTRY_ENABLE]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.enable.contract.test.ts\\n    disableExportRegistry:\\n      http: POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/disable\\n      requirements: [FR-007]\\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007]\\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/disable-export-registry.handler.ts\\n      db: [export_registries, export_audit_logs]\\n      worker: [future create requests must fail with TASK_DISABLED]\\n      audit: [REGISTRY_DISABLE]\\n      file: []\\n      tests:\\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.disable.contract.test.ts\\npaths:\\n  /export/tasks:\\n    post:\\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\\n      summary: Create export task\\n      description: |\\n        Creates a PENDING export task when taskCode is registered and enabled.\\n        clientRequestId is idempotent in scope tenantId + operatorId + taskCode + clientRequestId.\\n      operationId: createExportTask\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n      requestBody:\\n        required: true\\n        content:\\n          application/json:\\n            schema:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskRequest\\\"\\n            examples:\\n              purchaseOrder:\\n                summary: Purchase order export task\\n                value:\\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\\n                  subsystemCode: purchase\\n                  fileFormat: XLSX\\n                  clientRequestId: req-20260513-0001\\n                  queryParams:\\n                    createdAtFrom: \\\"2026-05-01T00:00:00+08:00\\\"\\n                    createdAtTo: \\\"2026-05-13T23:59:59+08:00\\\"\\n                    orderStatus: APPROVED\\n                    supplierId: SUP-001\\n                    purchaseOrgId: ORG-001\\n                    keyword: PO-2026\\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\\n        - TASK_DISABLED\\n        - EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\\n        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"201\\\":\\n          description: Task created.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope\\\"\\n              examples:\\n                created:\\n                  value:\\n                    code: SUCCESS\\n                    message: success\\n                    data:\\n                      taskId: exp_20260513_000001\\n                      taskCode: purchase-order-export\\n                      subsystemCode: purchase\\n                      status: PENDING\\n                      clientRequestId: req-20260513-0001\\n                      idempotencyHit: false\\n                      idempotencyScope: tenant-001:u001:purchase-order-export:req-20260513-0001\\n                      requestDigest: sha256:request-digest\\n                      configSnapshotDigest: sha256:config-digest\\n                      attemptNo: 0\\n                      createdAt: \\\"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\\\"\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Existing task returned for idempotent replay with identical request digest.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"400\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/CreateTaskBadRequest\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\\\"\\n        \\\"409\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/IdempotencyConflict\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/DatasourceUnavailable\\\"\\n      x-contract-errorResponseStatus:\\n        TASK_DISABLED: 400\\n        QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE: 400\\n        EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED: 400\\n        DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE: 500\\n        INTERNAL_ERROR: 500\\n    get:\\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\\n      summary: Search task history\\n      description: |\\n        Returns paged task history. Normal users can only see their own tasks;\\n        administrators can see global tasks according to roleCodes and orgScope.\\n      operationId: listExportTasks\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - name: taskCode\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n        - name: status\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\\\"\\n        - name: createdBy\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n        - name: createdAtFrom\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n            format: date-time\\n        - name: createdAtTo\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n            format: date-time\\n        - name: fileFormat\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\\\"\\n        - name: subsystemCode\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n        - name: page\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: integer\\n            minimum: 1\\n            default: 1\\n        - name: pageSize\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: integer\\n            minimum: 1\\n            maximum: 100\\n            default: 20\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Paged task history.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskPageEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/QueryExecutionError\\\"\\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}:\\n    get:\\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\\n      summary: Get task detail and progress\\n      operationId: getExportTask\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskId\\\"\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Task detail.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetailEnvelope\\\"\\n              examples:\\n                executing:\\n                  value:\\n                    code: SUCCESS\\n                    message: success\\n                    data:\\n                      taskId: exp_20260513_000001\\n                      taskCode: purchase-order-export\\n                      subsystemCode: purchase\\n                      status: EXECUTING\\n                      totalCount: 100000\\n                      processedCount: 20000\\n                      progressPercent: 20.0\\n                      fileFormat: ZIP\\n                      attemptNo: 1\\n                      requestId: req-20260513-0001\\n                      requestDigest: sha256:request-digest\\n                      configSnapshotDigest: sha256:config-digest\\n                      createdBy: u001\\n                      createdAt: \\\"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\\\"\\n                      updatedAt: \\\"2026-05-13T10:05:00+08:00\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/download:\\n    get:\\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\\n      summary: Download exported file\\n      description: |\\n        The default mode returns a signed URL and file metadata. Stream delivery\\n        is represented by application/octet-stream and equivalent metadata headers.\\n      operationId: downloadExportTask\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskId\\\"\\n        - name: mode\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\\\"\\n            default: SIGNED_URL\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Signed URL response or file stream.\\n          headers:\\n            X-Export-File-Name:\\n              schema:\\n                type: string\\n            X-Export-File-Size:\\n              schema:\\n                type: integer\\n                format: int64\\n            X-Export-Checksum:\\n              schema:\\n                type: string\\n            X-Export-Checksum-Algorithm:\\n              schema:\\n                type: string\\n                enum: [SHA-256]\\n            X-Export-Attempt-No:\\n              schema:\\n                type: integer\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/DownloadResponseEnvelope\\\"\\n              examples:\\n                signedUrl:\\n                  value:\\n                    code: SUCCESS\\n                    message: success\\n                    data:\\n                      deliveryMode: SIGNED_URL\\n                      downloadUrl: \\\"https://oss.example.com/signed-url\\\"\\n                      expiresAt: \\\"2026-05-13T10:10:00+08:00\\\"\\n                      fileName: purchase-order-export-20260513.zip\\n                      fileSize: 1048576\\n                      contentType: application/zip\\n                      checksum: sha256:file-checksum\\n                      checksumAlgorithm: SHA-256\\n                      storageKey: exports/purchase/purchase-order-export/20260513/exp_20260513_000001/1/purchase-order-export-20260513.zip\\n                      attemptNo: 1\\n            application/octet-stream:\\n              schema:\\n                type: string\\n                format: binary\\n        \\\"400\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/FileNotReady\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\\\"\\n        \\\"410\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/FileExpired\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/FileVerifyError\\\"\\n        \\\"502\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/ExportRenderError\\\"\\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\\n        - FILE_NOT_READY\\n        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\\n        - EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel:\\n    post:\\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\\n      summary: Cancel export task\\n      description: |\\n        PENDING tasks can be canceled immediately. EXECUTING tasks accept cancel\\n        intent and still return EXECUTING until the worker closes the task at a\\n        batch boundary. The API never returns an internal cancel marker as a task status.\\n      operationId: cancelExportTask\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskId\\\"\\n      requestBody:\\n        required: false\\n        content:\\n          application/json:\\n            schema:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskActionRequest\\\"\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Cancel accepted or completed.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponseEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"400\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InvalidTaskState\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/retry:\\n    post:\\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\\n      summary: Retry failed export task\\n      description: |\\n        Only FAILED tasks are retryable. Retry keeps the original taskId,\\n        reuses the original config snapshot, increments attemptNo and creates no\\n        second active execution attempt.\\n      operationId: retryExportTask\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskId\\\"\\n      requestBody:\\n        required: false\\n        content:\\n          application/json:\\n            schema:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskActionRequest\\\"\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Retry accepted.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponseEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"400\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InvalidTaskState\\\"\\n        \\\"409\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/ActiveAttemptConflict\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\n  /export/registries:\\n    post:\\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\\n      summary: Create export registry\\n      operationId: createExportRegistry\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n      requestBody:\\n        required: true\\n        content:\\n          application/json:\\n            schema:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\\\"\\n            examples:\\n              purchaseOrderRegistry:\\n                value:\\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\\n                  subsystemCode: purchase\\n                  displayName: Purchase order export\\n                  enabled: true\\n                  concurrencyLimit: 3\\n                  fileRetentionDays: 15\\n                  taskHistoryRetentionDays: 30\\n                  singleFileMaxRows: 20000\\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\\n                  supportedFormats: [XLSX, ZIP]\\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\\n                  parameterSchema:\\n                    required: [createdAtFrom, createdAtTo]\\n                    properties:\\n                      createdAtFrom:\\n                        type: string\\n                        format: date-time\\n                      createdAtTo:\\n                        type: string\\n                        format: date-time\\n                      orderStatus:\\n                        type: string\\n                      supplierId:\\n                        type: string\\n                      purchaseOrgId:\\n                        type: string\\n                      keyword:\\n                        type: string\\n                  queryTemplate:\\n                    queryTemplateVersion: v1\\n                    templateText: \\\"select ... where created_at between :createdAtFrom and :createdAtTo order by order_id asc\\\"\\n                    allowedParameters: [createdAtFrom, createdAtTo, orderStatus, supplierId, purchaseOrgId, keyword]\\n                  fieldMappings:\\n                    - fieldCode: orderNo\\n                      headerName: Order No\\n                      fieldType: STRING\\n                      orderNo: 1\\n                      sensitive: false\\n                      exportable: true\\n                    - fieldCode: contactPhone\\n                      headerName: Contact Phone\\n                      fieldType: STRING\\n                      orderNo: 10\\n                      sensitive: true\\n                      exportable: true\\n                      maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\\n                  maskingPolicy:\\n                    rules:\\n                      phone_mask:\\n                        type: PHONE\\n                        preservePrefix: 3\\n                        preserveSuffix: 4\\n                  dataScopeTemplate: \\\"tenant_id = :tenantId and org_id in (:orgScope)\\\"\\n                  cursorField: orderId\\n                  orderBy:\\n                    - field: orderId\\n                      direction: ASC\\n                  batchSize: 1000\\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\\n        - REGISTRY_CONFLICT\\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"201\\\":\\n          description: Registry created.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"400\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/RegistryBadRequest\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"409\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/RegistryConflict\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/RegistryServerError\\\"\\n    get:\\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\\n      summary: List export registries\\n      operationId: listExportRegistries\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - name: taskCode\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n        - name: subsystemCode\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: string\\n        - name: enabled\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: boolean\\n        - name: page\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: integer\\n            minimum: 1\\n            default: 1\\n        - name: pageSize\\n          in: query\\n          schema:\\n            type: integer\\n            minimum: 1\\n            maximum: 100\\n            default: 20\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Paged registry list.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryPageEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}:\\n    get:\\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\\n      summary: Get export registry\\n      operationId: getExportRegistry\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\\\"\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Registry detail.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\n    put:\\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\\n      summary: Update export registry\\n      description: Registry updates only affect tasks created after the update.\\n      operationId: updateExportRegistry\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\\\"\\n      requestBody:\\n        required: true\\n        content:\\n          application/json:\\n            schema:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\\\"\\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Registry updated.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"400\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/RegistryBadRequest\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/RegistryServerError\\\"\\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}/enable:\\n    post:\\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\\n      summary: Enable export registry\\n      operationId: enableExportRegistry\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\\\"\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Registry enabled.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}/disable:\\n    post:\\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\\n      summary: Disable export registry\\n      operationId: disableExportRegistry\\n      parameters:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\\\"\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\\\"\\n      responses:\\n        \\\"200\\\":\\n          description: Registry disabled.\\n          content:\\n            application/json:\\n              schema:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\\\"\\n        \\\"401\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\\\"\\n        \\\"403\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\\\"\\n        \\\"404\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\\\"\\n        \\\"500\\\":\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/responses/InternalError\\\"\\ncomponents:\\n  securitySchemes:\\n    OperatorId:\\n      type: apiKey\\n      in: header\\n      name: X-Operator-Id\\n      description: Authenticated operator id forwarded by gateway or caller.\\n    TenantId:\\n      type: apiKey\\n      in: header\\n      name: X-Tenant-Id\\n      description: Tenant id forwarded by gateway or caller.\\n    RoleCodes:\\n      type: apiKey\\n      in: header\\n      name: X-Role-Codes\\n      description: Comma-separated role codes forwarded by gateway or caller.\\n    OrgScope:\\n      type: apiKey\\n      in: header\\n      name: X-Org-Scope\\n      description: Organization scope forwarded by gateway or caller.\\n    RequestId:\\n      type: apiKey\\n      in: header\\n      name: X-Request-Id\\n      description: Request id used by audit logs and task events.\\n  parameters:\\n    XOperatorId:\\n      name: X-Operator-Id\\n      in: header\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n      description: Authenticated operator id.\\n    XTenantId:\\n      name: X-Tenant-Id\\n      in: header\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n      description: Tenant id for task visibility and data scope.\\n    XRoleCodes:\\n      name: X-Role-Codes\\n      in: header\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n      description: Comma-separated role codes.\\n    XOrgScope:\\n      name: X-Org-Scope\\n      in: header\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n      description: Organization scope expression or encoded scope list.\\n    XRequestId:\\n      name: X-Request-Id\\n      in: header\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n      description: Upstream request id used by audit logs and task events.\\n    TaskId:\\n      name: taskId\\n      in: path\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n    TaskCode:\\n      name: taskCode\\n      in: path\\n      required: true\\n      schema:\\n        type: string\\n  responses:\\n    AuthContextMissing:\\n      description: Required auth context is missing or malformed.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            authMissing:\\n              value:\\n                code: AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING\\n                message: auth context missing\\n                data: null\\n    PermissionDenied:\\n      description: Operator has no permission for the task, registry or file.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            denied:\\n              value:\\n                code: PERMISSION_DENIED\\n                message: permission denied\\n                data: null\\n    TaskNotFound:\\n      description: Task not found or invisible to current operator.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            notFound:\\n              value:\\n                code: TASK_NOT_FOUND\\n                message: task not found\\n                data: null\\n    TaskNotRegistered:\\n      description: taskCode is not registered.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            notRegistered:\\n              value:\\n                code: TASK_NOT_REGISTERED\\n                message: task code not registered\\n                data: null\\n    CreateTaskBadRequest:\\n      description: Create task request is invalid, disabled or exceeds configured limits.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            validation:\\n              value:\\n                code: VALIDATION_ERROR\\n                message: validation failed\\n                data: null\\n                errors:\\n                  - field: taskCode\\n                    reason: required\\n            taskDisabled:\\n              value:\\n                code: TASK_DISABLED\\n                message: task code is disabled\\n                data:\\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\\n            queryParamsTooLarge:\\n              value:\\n                code: QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE\\n                message: queryParams exceeds 32768 bytes\\n                data: null\\n            exportLimitExceeded:\\n              value:\\n                code: EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\\n                message: export limit exceeded\\n                data:\\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\\n    IdempotencyConflict:\\n      description: Same idempotency scope with different request digest.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            conflict:\\n              value:\\n                code: IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT\\n                message: clientRequestId conflicts with a different request digest\\n                data:\\n                  idempotencyScope: tenant-001:u001:purchase-order-export:req-20260513-0001\\n    InvalidTaskState:\\n      description: Operation is not allowed for current official task status.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            invalidRetry:\\n              value:\\n                code: INVALID_TASK_STATE\\n                message: current task status does not allow this operation\\n                data:\\n                  status: EXECUTING\\n    ActiveAttemptConflict:\\n      description: Another active execution attempt already exists.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            activeAttempt:\\n              value:\\n                code: ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT\\n                message: active execution attempt already exists\\n                data:\\n                  taskId: exp_20260513_000001\\n                  attemptNo: 1\\n    FileExpired:\\n      description: File is expired or marked as not downloadable.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            expired:\\n              value:\\n                code: FILE_EXPIRED\\n                message: file expired\\n                data: null\\n    FileNotReady:\\n      description: File is not published or the task is not completed yet.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            notReady:\\n              value:\\n                code: FILE_NOT_READY\\n                message: file is not ready for download\\n                data:\\n                  status: EXECUTING\\n    FileVerifyError:\\n      description: File upload, metadata or checksum verification failed before publish.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            verifyFailed:\\n              value:\\n                code: FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\\n                message: file verification failed\\n                data:\\n                  checksumAlgorithm: SHA-256\\n    DatasourceUnavailable:\\n      description: Datasource or datasource credential is unavailable.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            datasourceUnavailable:\\n              value:\\n                code: DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\\n                message: datasource unavailable\\n                data:\\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\\n    QueryExecutionError:\\n      description: Query execution failed, batch retries exhausted or cursor contract violated.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            queryFailed:\\n              value:\\n                code: QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR\\n                message: query execution failed\\n                data:\\n                  cursorField: orderId\\n    RegistryBadRequest:\\n      description: Registry request is invalid, exceeds limits, or contains invalid field/masking configuration.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            validation:\\n              value:\\n                code: VALIDATION_ERROR\\n                message: validation failed\\n                data: null\\n            exportLimitExceeded:\\n              value:\\n                code: EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\\n                message: export limit exceeded\\n                data:\\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\\n            fieldMappingInvalid:\\n              value:\\n                code: FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\\n                message: field mapping invalid\\n                data:\\n                  fieldCode: contactPhone\\n            maskingRuleError:\\n              value:\\n                code: MASKING_RULE_ERROR\\n                message: masking rule error\\n                data:\\n                  maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\\n    RegistryServerError:\\n      description: Registry contract references an invalid query template, datasource, field mapping or masking backend.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            queryTemplateInvalid:\\n              value:\\n                code: QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\\n                message: query template invalid\\n                data:\\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\\n            datasourceUnavailable:\\n              value:\\n                code: DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\\n                message: datasource unavailable\\n                data:\\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\\n            fieldMappingInvalid:\\n              value:\\n                code: FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\\n                message: field mapping invalid\\n                data:\\n                  fieldCode: contactPhone\\n            maskingRuleError:\\n              value:\\n                code: MASKING_RULE_ERROR\\n                message: masking rule error\\n                data:\\n                  maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\\n    ExportRenderError:\\n      description: XLSX or ZIP render failed.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            renderFailed:\\n              value:\\n                code: EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\\n                message: export render error\\n                data:\\n                  fileFormat: ZIP\\n    RegistryConflict:\\n      description: Registry taskCode already exists or conflicts with immutable fields.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            duplicate:\\n              value:\\n                code: REGISTRY_CONFLICT\\n                message: taskCode already exists\\n                data: null\\n    InternalError:\\n      description: Unclassified server-side error. Specific platform errors should use a more precise response when known.\\n      content:\\n        application/json:\\n          schema:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\\\"\\n          examples:\\n            internalError:\\n              value:\\n                code: INTERNAL_ERROR\\n                message: internal error\\n                data: null\\n  schemas:\\n    ResponseCode:\\n      type: string\\n      enum:\\n        - SUCCESS\\n        - VALIDATION_ERROR\\n        - AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING\\n        - PERMISSION_DENIED\\n        - TASK_NOT_FOUND\\n        - TASK_NOT_REGISTERED\\n        - TASK_DISABLED\\n        - QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE\\n        - IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT\\n        - INVALID_TASK_STATE\\n        - FILE_EXPIRED\\n        - FILE_NOT_READY\\n        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\\n        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\\n        - QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR\\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\\n        - EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\\n        - EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\\n        - REGISTRY_CONFLICT\\n        - ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT\\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\\n    TaskStatus:\\n      type: string\\n      description: Official public task status. Internal cancel flags are not valid values.\\n      enum: [PENDING, EXECUTING, COMPLETED, FAILED, CANCELED, EXPIRED]\\n    FileFormat:\\n      type: string\\n      enum: [XLSX, ZIP]\\n    DeliveryMode:\\n      type: string\\n      enum: [SIGNED_URL, STREAM]\\n    Envelope:\\n      type: object\\n      required: [code, message]\\n      properties:\\n        code:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\\\"\\n        message:\\n          type: string\\n    ErrorEnvelope:\\n      allOf:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/Envelope\\\"\\n        - type: object\\n          properties:\\n            data:\\n              type: object\\n              nullable: true\\n              additionalProperties: true\\n            errors:\\n              type: array\\n              items:\\n                $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/FieldError\\\"\\n    FieldError:\\n      type: object\\n      required: [field, reason]\\n      properties:\\n        field:\\n          type: string\\n        reason:\\n          type: string\\n    CreateExportTaskRequest:\\n      type: object\\n      required: [taskCode, subsystemCode, fileFormat, queryParams]\\n      properties:\\n        taskCode:\\n          type: string\\n        subsystemCode:\\n          type: string\\n        fileFormat:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\\\"\\n        clientRequestId:\\n          type: string\\n          maxLength: 128\\n          description: Optional idempotency key scoped by tenantId/operatorId/taskCode.\\n        queryParams:\\n          type: object\\n          additionalProperties: true\\n          description: Must match registry parameter schema and must not exceed 32768 bytes after canonical JSON serialization.\\n        deliveryPreference:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\\\"\\n    CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope:\\n      allOf:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/Envelope\\\"\\n        - type: object\\n          required: [data]\\n          properties:\\n            data:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponse\\\"\\n    CreateExportTaskResponse:\\n      type: object\\n      required:\\n        - taskId\\n        - taskCode\\n        - subsystemCode\\n        - status\\n        - idempotencyScope\\n        - requestDigest\\n        - configSnapshotDigest\\n        - attemptNo\\n        - createdAt\\n      properties:\\n        taskId:\\n          type: string\\n        taskCode:\\n          type: string\\n        subsystemCode:\\n          type: string\\n        status:\\n          type: string\\n          enum: [PENDING]\\n        clientRequestId:\\n          type: string\\n        idempotencyHit:\\n          type: boolean\\n        idempotencyScope:\\n          type: string\\n          description: Stable success-response evidence for the tenantId + operatorId + taskCode + clientRequestId idempotency scope.\\n        requestDigest:\\n          type: string\\n        configSnapshotDigest:\\n          type: string\\n        attemptNo:\\n          type: integer\\n          minimum: 0\\n        createdAt:\\n          type: string\\n          format: date-time\\n    ExportTaskDetailEnvelope:\\n      allOf:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/Envelope\\\"\\n        - type: object\\n          required: [data]\\n          properties:\\n            data:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetail\\\"\\n    ExportTaskDetail:\\n      type: object\\n      required:\\n        - taskId\\n        - taskCode\\n        - subsystemCode\\n        - status\\n        - totalCount\\n        - processedCount\\n        - progressPercent\\n        - attemptNo\\n        - requestId\\n        - requestDigest\\n        - configSnapshotDigest\\n        - createdBy\\n        - createdAt\\n        - updatedAt\\n      properties:\\n        taskId:\\n          type: string\\n        taskCode:\\n          type: string\\n        subsystemCode:\\n          type: string\\n        status:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\\\"\\n        totalCount:\\n          type: integer\\n          format: int64\\n          minimum: 0\\n        processedCount:\\n          type: integer\\n          format: int64\\n          minimum: 0\\n        progressPercent:\\n          type: number\\n          minimum: 0\\n          maximum: 100\\n        fileFormat:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\\\"\\n        attemptNo:\\n          type: integer\\n          minimum: 0\\n        errorCode:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\\\"\\n        errorMessage:\\n          type: string\\n        failureStage:\\n          type: string\\n        lastSuccessStage:\\n          type: string\\n        requestId:\\n          type: string\\n        requestDigest:\\n          type: string\\n        configSnapshotDigest:\\n          type: string\\n        createdBy:\\n          type: string\\n        createdAt:\\n          type: string\\n          format: date-time\\n        updatedAt:\\n          type: string\\n          format: date-time\\n        file:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/FileMetadata\\\"\\n        batchCheckpoint:\\n          $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/BatchCheckpoint\\\"\\n        recentEvents:\\n          type: array\\n          items:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/TaskEvent\\\"\\n        auditEvents:\\n          type: array\\n          items:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/AuditEvent\\\"\\n    ExportTaskPageEnvelope:\\n      allOf:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/Envelope\\\"\\n        - type: object\\n          required: [data]\\n          properties:\\n            data:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskPage\\\"\\n    ExportTaskPage:\\n      type: object\\n      required: [items, page, pageSize, total]\\n      properties:\\n        items:\\n          type: array\\n          items:\\n            $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetail\\\"\\n        page:\\n          type: integer\\n        pageSize:\\n          type: integer\\n        total:\\n          type: integer\\n          format: int64\\n    DownloadResponseEnvelope:\\n      allOf:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/Envelope\\\"\\n        - type: object\\n          required: [data]\\n          properties:\\n            data:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/DownloadResponse\\\"\\n    DownloadResponse:\\n      allOf:\\n        - $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/FileMetadata\\\"\\n        - type: object\\n          required: [deliveryMode, expiresAt]\\n          properties:\\n            deliveryMode:\\n              $ref: \\\"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\\\"\\n            downloadUrl:\\n              type: string\\n              format: uri\\n            expiresAt:\\n              type: string\\n              format: d